\id 2JN - Biblica® Open Ndebele Contemporary Bible 
\h 2 UJohane 
\toc1 Incwadi Yesibili KaJohane 
\toc2 2 UJohane 
\toc3 2Joh 
\mt2 Incwadi Yesibili 
\mt1 KaJohane 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Mina omdala, 
\b  
\p Ngilobela inkosikazi ekhethiweyo labantwana bayo, engibathandayo eqinisweni, kungayisimi kuphela, kodwa labo bonke abalaziyo iqiniso,  
\v 2 ngenxa yeqiniso elikhona kithi njalo elizakuba lathi kuze kube nininini: 
\b  
\p  
\v 3 Umusa, lesihawu kanye lokuthula okuvela kuNkulunkulu uBaba lakuJesu Khristu, iNdodana kaBaba, kuzakuba lathi ngeqiniso langothando. 
\b  
\b  
\p  
\v 4 Kungithokozise kakhulu ukufumana abanye babantwana benu bephila ngeqiniso njengokulaywa kwethu nguBaba.  
\v 5 Khathesi-ke, nkosikazi ethandekayo, ngikulobela umlayo omutsha, kodwa esasilawo kusukela ekuqaleni. Ngicela ukuba sithandane.  
\v 6 Uthando yilolu: ukuba siphile ngokulalela imilayo yakhe. Njengoba uzwile kusukela ekuqaleni, umlayo wakhe yikuthi uphile impilo yothando. 
\p  
\v 7 Ngitsho lokhu ngoba abakhohlisi abanengi abangavumiyo ukuthi uJesu Khristu weza engumuntu sebekhona emhlabeni. Lowomuntu onjalo ungumkhohlisi lomphikuKhristu.  
\v 8 Qaphelani ukuba lingalahlekelwa yilokho elakusebenzelayo, kodwa ukuba liphiwe umvuzo ngokupheleleyo.  
\v 9 Lowo odlulela phambili angabe esaqhubeka ngemfundiso kaKhristu kalaye uNkulunkulu; lowo oqhubekayo ngemfundiso uloBaba leNdodana.  
\v 10 Nxa umuntu esiza kini engalethi imfundiso le, lingamngenisi ezindlini zenu njalo lingamamukeli.  
\v 11 Lowo omamukelayo uyahlanganyela emisebenzini yakhe emibi. 
\b  
\b  
\p  
\v 12 Ngilokunengi engingalilobela khona, kodwa angifuni ukusebenzisa iphepha le-inki. Kodwa ngithemba ukuthi ngizalethekelela ngikhulume lani sikhangelene ukuze intokozo yethu iphelele. 
\b  
\p  
\v 13 Abantwana bakadadewenu okhethiweyo bayakubingelela.